'''Umugezi wa Rubyiro''' ni uruzi rwo mu [[Intara y'amajyepfo|majyepfo]] y'[[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|uburengerazuba]] bwu [[Rwanda]] ni uruzi rw'ibumoso rw'umugezi wa Ruzizi. Ihurira na Ruzizi, igize umupaka uhuza u [[Rwanda]] na [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo,]] nko mu birometero 2 uvuye aho umugezi wa Ruhwa ugize umupaka uhuza u [[Rwanda]] n'[[Uburundi]].<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rubyiro_River</ref><ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rubyiro_River#CITEREFRusizi_Administrative_Map</ref>

